dc_title_s: Survey of plot 2 & parts of plots 1, 4, 5 & 6, block 460 together with lots 1 to 30, inclusive, block 460a, tax assessment map, township of North Bergen, Hudson County, N.J.
dc_description_s: Tax assessment map delineating Bellman's Creek through properties on Block 460 in North Bergen Township, New Jersey|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Note on map states "Part of the northerly and part of the easterly boundary of the property surveyed are fixed by the monumentation of a certain map entitled Map No. 1"
